    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Ye an-gel-ic hosts, go ye on the way be-fore__ us, ye that be in Beth--le-hem, make the man-ger read--y. The Word of God__ is born; the Ho-ly Wis---dom now com-eth forth. Church, re-ceive the greet-ing; and up-on this re-joic-ing of the The--o-to-kos, let us peo-ple cry: Bless-ed art Thou Who art now come; our God,__ glo-ry be to__ Thee.__"
